{% comment %}
  Renders an image tag using Shopify's image_tag filter

  Accepts:
  - image: {Object} Image Object
  - image_width: {String} Size of the product image card. Values are pixels
  - image_class: {String} Class attribute of the returning image tag (optional)
  - image_loading: {String} Loading attribute of the returning image tag (optional)
  
  Usage:
  {% render 'card-product-image', image: card_product.featured_media, image_width: card_product.featured_media.width, image_class: 'motion-reduce large-up-hide', image_loading: 'loading="lazy"' %}
{% endcomment %}

